## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0de87-103"><xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase>类是抽象基类按钮字段，并且包含的方法和属性所共有的所有按钮字段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0de87-103">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase> class is the abstract base class for button fields and contains the methods and properties that are common to all button fields.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0de87-104">由于此类是抽象的不能直接创建它的一个实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0de87-104">Because this class is abstract, you cannot create an instance of it directly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0de87-105">相反，必须创建继承自非抽象类的实例<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase>类，如<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonField>或<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CommandField>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0de87-105">Instead, you must create an instance of a non-abstract class that inherits from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase> class, such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonField> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CommandField> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0de87-106">一个对象，派生自<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase>由数据绑定控件 (如<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>和<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>控件) 显示为显示每个记录的一个或多个按钮。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0de87-106">An object that is derived from the  <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase> is used by data-bound controls (such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> controls) to display one or more buttons for each record that is displayed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0de87-107">具体取决于使用它的数据绑定控件显示按钮字段的方式不同。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0de87-107">A button field is displayed differently depending on the data-bound control in which it is used.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0de87-108">例如，<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>控件将按钮字段显示为一个列，而<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>控件将其显示为一行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0de87-108">For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control displays a button field as a column, whereas the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> control displays it as a row.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0de87-109">单击按钮字段中的按钮会导致父数据绑定控件的命令事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0de87-109">Clicking a button in a button field raises the command event of the parent data-bound control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0de87-110">您可以通过为命令事件提供事件处理程序中单击某个按钮时要执行的自定义的例程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0de87-110">You can provide a custom routine to perform when a button is clicked by providing an event handler for the command event.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="0de87-111"><xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>控件将引发<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.RowCommand>事件，而<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>控件引发<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.ItemCommand>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0de87-111">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.RowCommand> event, whereas the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> control raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.ItemCommand> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0de87-112">若要指定要显示的按钮类型，请使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase.ButtonType%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0de87-112">To specify the type of button to display, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase.ButtonType%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0de87-113">若要显示或隐藏的页眉节<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase>对象，设置<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase.ShowHeader%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0de87-113">To show or hide the header section of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase> object, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase.ShowHeader%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
